Package: smithproxy
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
                            libstdc++6 (>= 8.3.0),
                            libssl3 (>=3.0.0),
                            libconfig++9v5,
                            libmicrohttpd12,
                            libpam0g,
                            libcurl4,
                            iptables,
                            python3,
                            python3-pip,
                            python3-setuptools,
                            python3-wheel,
                            python3-cryptography,
                            python3-pyroute2,
                            iproute2,
                            telnet
Description:
 Feature-rich, fast transparent TCP/UDP/TLS proxy.
 Forwarded traffic is diverted to smithproxy where it's processed based
 on policies with feature profiles.
 It can also process local traffic and accepts SOCKS5 requests.
